CreateLogExport.document:
API domain name: `rum.tencentcloudapi.com`.

This API is used to create a log download task.

Default API request rate limit: 20 requests/sec.
CreateLogExport.name: Creates log download task

CreateOfflineLogConfig.document: This API is used to create an offline log listener to report offline logs of particular users.
CreateOfflineLogConfig.name: Creates offline log listener

CreateProject.document: This API is used to create a project (owned by the specified team).
CreateProject.name: Creates project

CreateReleaseFile.document: This API is used to create a file record for the specified project.
CreateReleaseFile.name: Creates release file record

CreateStarProject.document: This API is used to add a starred project.
CreateStarProject.name: Adds starred project

CreateTawInstance.document: This API is used to create a RUM instance.
CreateTawInstance.name: Creates RUM instance

CreateWhitelist.document: This API is used to create an allowlist.
CreateWhitelist.name: Creates allowlist

DeleteInstance.document: This API is used to delete an instance. The deleted instance cannot be recovered.
DeleteInstance.name: Deletes instance

DeleteLogExport.document:
API domain name: `rum.tencentcloudapi.com`.

This API is used to delete a log download task.

Default API request rate limit: 20 requests/sec.
DeleteLogExport.name: Deletes log download task

DeleteOfflineLogConfig.document: This API is used to delete an offline RUM log listener. Then, offline logs of particular users will not be reported.
DeleteOfflineLogConfig.name: Deletes offline RUM log listener

DeleteOfflineLogRecord.document: This API is used to delete an offline log record.
DeleteOfflineLogRecord.name: Deletes offline log record

DeleteProject.document: This API is used to delete the specified RUM project.
DeleteProject.name: Deletes RUM project

DeleteReleaseFile.document: This API is used to delete the specified sourcemap file.
DeleteReleaseFile.name: Deletes release file

DeleteStarProject.document: This API is used to delete a starred project for the specified user.
DeleteStarProject.name: Deletes starred project

DeleteWhitelist.document: This API is used to delete an allowlist.
DeleteWhitelist.name: Deletes allowlist
